x4freetext: -SLOW NEUTRON SCATTERING LENGTHS OF THE ISOTOPES
FRM IS AN OPEN POOL REACTOR WITH A THERMAL
.THE SILVER ISOTOPES USED WERE METALIC POWDER OR
THIN WIRES ALL WITH PURITIES GREATER THAN 99.99
SCATTERING DENSITY OF A POWDERED SAMPLE WITH THAT
OF A RANGE OF LIQUID MIXTURES OF VARIED BUT WELL
SCATTERED NEUTRONS FROM THE CHRISTIANSEN FILTER.
.THE UNCERTAINTY IN THE ORDER OF 1 PERCENT FOR THE
MEAN SCATTERING LENGTHS IS MAINLY DUE TO THE COR-
RECTION AND THE UNCERTAINTY OF THE DENSITY.
